Was this something from the talks with winnie the pooh last week? -Whatever happened to those talks of the Doge check talks? Or the audit of Fort Knox? -no arrests of the deep state for their roles in J6 Sure we have had some wins, but they have felt minor when the big stuff people voted for seems to have been backburnered or ignored. Did the deep state get to Trump? Or is he making the same mistake as last term and surronding himself with people who are sabotaging him?
